If you are going to fear kite... just use fear.  
<br />

<br />
Though fear kiting is only good for like 6 level then charm kiting takes over.
<br />

<br />
Charm kiting will last you for about 30 levels then DoT kiting become a better option.  
<br />

<br />
The DPS with fear kiting is not all taht good.  The only time I would say go for it is if you are in a all dps group with someone that can snare.  Then it can be fun.  Assuming it doesn't drive everyone nuts first.</span></td>
